<HEADLINE>
A 100 YEARS LATER, CAN FREUD BE TAKEN SERIOUSLY? 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By KENNETH LaFAVE  
 c.1999 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; (THIS ARTICLE ALSO MOVED IN ``A'' and ``K'' CATEGORIES)
