<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-07 22:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2089 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s BC-RUN-RHODEN-COLUMN-NYT     11-07 0861
