<HEADLINE>
PRODUCT REVIEWS FROM ANYONE WITH AN OPINION
</HEADLINE>
  By BOB TEDESCHI 
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features)
<TEXT>
<P>
   (To purchase this ``separate buy'' article from the New York
Times Syndicate please contact syndicate sales representative DEBRA
WEYDERT at 732-390-4480)
</P>
<P>
   Traditionally, advice on consumer purchasing decisions has been
the province of print publications like Consumer Reports, PC
