trillions of dollars would make him ``the second most powerful
person in our whole government,'' a daunting thought, in part since
Lew does not appear to have aged much since college. The power is
real and Lew, knee-deep in politics since he was 12 years old,
wants to use it. ``The purpose of power is to get things done,''
